\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs28 6.\tab Backlog of Ideas\par
\pard\li360\sa200\b0\fs24 This is a very terse list of ideas for improving Touchless SDK.\ul\b\par
\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\ulnone ColorLib\par
\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li1440\b0 Improve HSV colorspace partitioning model. We could group perceived similar colors better. Potentially replace with a group clustering algorithm. Perhaps just refine the per-dimension bin counts, or replace the hash function.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Use a lookup table instead of transforming RGB to HSV. We can just terminate early if it\rquote s not in the lookup table.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Reduce loop overhead of converting ARGB values into RGB values, then into HSV values, then into Binned HSV values, then finally into a hash # for color lookup during marker update. Potentially use a lookup table for a subset of colors to avoid the math altogether.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Improve HSV color grouping, consider refining the per-dimension bin counts or using a different HSV color-space partitioning model that better suits human perception of similar colors.\par
\pard\li1440\par
\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\b Marker\par
\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li1440\b0 Implement a way of getting higher degree moments of inertia. Mostly, we are interested in the axis of least rotational momentum and the roundness factor.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Allow the user to send a mask image with the add marker bitmap for arbitrary marker region selections.\rdblquote\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Extend or replace alpha smoothing with exponential decay to provide smoothed marker data and reduce the marker jumpiness.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Optimize threshold, or replace threshold concept with a partial matching. Also, step threshold by numbers that actually make a difference, or just have sensitivity +/- buttons and increment functions\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Expose smoothing factor as a public marker property.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Fix and improve the automated  marker tests\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Standardize some marker colors, create an \ldblquote auto-find makers\rdblquote\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Improve the search bounds of a previously absent marker. \par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Improve the meta-tracking (cases where small numbers of pixels are missing from the middle of a marker, or are outliers of the concentration of pixels)\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Periodically/continuously adopt surrounding pixels of confirmed marker pixels\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Coloravg is currently just marker representative color. Implement a way of actually getting a color average from the set of colors found\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Improve Marker highlighting\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Improve upon the raster scan algorithm used for marker updating.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Optimize the method for getting the marker appearance from a circular area of a bitmap; we could use hierarchical bounds intersection or something smarter than the current scan algorithm.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Optimize the values used to increment/decrement color frequencies for marker appearance detection. This should be somehow based on signal/noise ratios.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Improve the expected marker regions used for scanning on update. We could consider the marker\rquote s acceleration, rather than just the velocity. Perhaps try using regions that aren\rquote t axis-aligned rectangles. \par
\pard\li1440\par
\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\b TouchlessMgr\par
\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li1440\b0 Add functionality to save and load marker configuration files (reduce repeat training of the same marker, possibly provide autoconfig files for standard markers... will variant lighting allow for this?)\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Implement additional marker data such as ColorAverage, ColorSpace, Axis and Roundness.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Add flood fill algorithm so we can add a marker with a few points in the Bitmap.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Refine the marker tracked colors as we find colors around the marker. \par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}The representative color doesn\rquote t always match the perceived color of the marker.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Provide subsequent examples of a marker appearance\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Have TouchlessMgr actually expose a way to get a list of the current markers\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Make a better exception for camera start failure\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Validate the PixelFormat of incoming images.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Create a utility function to retrieve ImageData in a consistent manner; we have a bit of code duplication right now.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Make a public interface for demo classes to implement, then allow the user to just invoke start and stop of a demo class on the library\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Standardize error handling and exception generation across the project.\par
